content:
Activate your Commerce store to share it with colleagues without setting up a custom domain. This allows you to see what the store looks like before going live. When ready, configure the CDN and custom domain for optimal performance and security. The activate function has been expanded so that publishing the store is automatic when activated.

Where: B2B Commerce and D2C Commerce in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
title: Activate Commerce Store Without Custom Domain
